# Template (`shaper_helixultimate`)

## Entry (`index.php`)

```php
require_once JPATH_PLUGINS . '/system/helixultimate/bootstrap.php';
$theme = new HelixUltimate\Framework\Core\HelixUltimate;
// load params via Helper::loadTemplateData()
$theme->add_scss('master', $scssVars, 'template');
$theme->render_layout();
```

Do not skip bootstrap. Prefer `Helper::loadTemplateData()` / `flushSettingsDataToJs()` for params → frontend (`Joomla.getOptions('data')`).

## Features

- File: `features/{name}.php` → class `HelixUltimateFeature{Name}`
- Required: `$position`, `$load_pos`, `renderFeature()`
- Loaded by `HelixUltimate::include_features()` scanning `features/*.php`

## Assets

- Styles: SCSS via `$theme->add_scss()` (see helix-scss rule). Avoid one-off root CSS.
- Scripts: `js/` — Vanilla ES6, `DOMContentLoaded`, `fetch` (not jQuery.ajax).
- Prefer `data-*` hooks over hard-coded selectors.
- Custom dirs auto-scanned: `css/custom/`, `js/custom/`, `scss/custom/`.

## Config

- Positions / manifest: `templateDetails.xml`
- Full options UI: `options.xml` (`addfieldpath` → plugin `src/fields`)
- Defaults / layout JSON: `options.json`
- Headers / offcanvas: `headers/`, `offcanvas/`

## Overrides

Site view changes → `html/` (Joomla hierarchy). Framework-wide → plugin `overrides/`. Never core.
